Login to root
You will need to do:
sudo passwd root

Then go ahead to set password. Use the root user using
$ su root
==========================================================
delete folder command :
$ rm -rf lampp
===================================
run sublime in root
$ sudo -H subl
$ sudo -i subl
===================================
Network problem
$ sudo service network-manager stop
$ sudo service network-manager start
===================================
